Author: focus_ana
Text: You need to take time to let your stress level itself out. Taking an adderall (no matter what dosage) will only intensify everything you are currently feeling prior to taking the medication. It is a stimulant, I understand the feeling of not wanting to eat, but you are going to cause yourself to have an anxiety attack. This is only going to make things worse. So rest up and start again when you feel brand new!
